Source: libpasastro
Priority: optional
Maintainer: pch <pch@ap-i.net>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>=9), libc6-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Section: libs
Homepage: https://sourceforge.net/projects/libpasastro/

Package: libpasastro-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: libpasastro (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}, libc6-dev
Description: Interface Pascal program with standard astronomy libraries.
 libpasgetdss.so : Interface with GetDSS to work with DSS images.
 libpasplan404.so: Interface with Plan404 to compute planets position.
 libpaswcs.so : Interface with libwcs to work with FITS WCS.


